feed.subtitle: Hi! My name is Wojciech Florczak and I want to become professional programmer. On this site you can look at my latest projects hosted directly from my GitHub repositories by GitHub Pages.

entry.title: My Portfolio
entry.content:
My first Front-End project is this portfolio site. Every project is hosted directly from my GitHub repository github.com/WojtasF
